  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428300/extras/dbc9bb47a9b05aa1aeb609db306f4057.poster.avif?t=1716422916\" width=516 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428300/extras/dbc9bb47a9b05aa1aeb609db306f4057.webm?t=1716422916\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428300/extras/e8d50b8b77af02e6bc6168e4cf006bda.avif?t=1716422916\" width=590 height=84 /></span><br>Play solo or party with friends in this cute, cooperative combination of tower defense and beat 'em up action! Travel through time, leap through levels, quickly construct trusty towers, and battle against wave after wave of zany enemies!<br><br><strong>Will you become a master of Chrono-Fu and save the world from evil?</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428300/extras/e514b2004c517a0a8e93195baa8acb92.webp?t=1716422916\" width=25 height=15 /></span>Play as adorable, humble heroes! <i>(Custodian, Cook, Gardener, Fixer, Deliverer, Nurse)</i></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428300/extras/e514b2004c517a0a8e93195baa8acb92.webp?t=1716422916\" width=25 height=15 /></span>Bash baddies, build towers and battle bosses in three unique times in history!</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428300/extras/e514b2004c517a0a8e93195baa8acb92.webp?t=1716422916\" width=25 height=15 /></span>Accelerate and slow the flow of time in each level to achieve maximum victory!</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428300/extras/e514b2004c517a0a8e93195baa8acb92.webp?t=1716422916\" width=25 height=15 /></span>Unlock an arsenal of stylish shoes, wacky weapons, powerful pets and beverage boosts! </ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428300/extras/e514b2004c517a0a8e93195baa8acb92.webp?t=1716422916\" width=25 height=15 /></span>Loveable, light-hearted and fast-paced fun for all ages and skill levels!</ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428300/extras/e514b2004c517a0a8e93195baa8acb92.webp?t=1716422916\" width=25 height=15 /></span>Keyboard support for 1 player.</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428300/extras/e514b2004c517a0a8e93195baa8acb92.webp?t=1716422916\" width=25 height=15 /></span>Controller support for 1-4 players.</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428300/extras/e514b2004c517a0a8e93195baa8acb92.webp?t=1716422916\" width=25 height=15 /></span>(at least one controller required for local multiplayer)</ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428300/extras/679e732c5cc9727baffb14d587399e52.avif?t=1716422916\" width=473 height=84 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428300/extras/60f1421c8912eff9a3dde23224899a43.poster.avif?t=1716422916\" width=516 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428300/extras/60f1421c8912eff9a3dde23224899a43.webm?t=1716422916\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
