h level to achieve maximum victory!</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428300/extras/e514b2004c517a0a8e93195baa8acb92.webp?t=1716422916\" width=25 height=15 /></span>Unlock an arsenal of stylish shoes, wacky weapons, powerful pets and beverage boosts! </ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428300/extras/e514b2004c517a0a8e93195baa8acb92.webp?t=1716422916\" width=25 height=15 /></span>Loveable, light-hearted and fast-paced fun for all ages and skill levels!</ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428300/extras/e514b2004c517a0a8e93195baa8acb92.webp?t=1716422916\" width=25 height=15 /></span>Keyboard support for 1 player.</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428300/extras/e514b2004c517a0a8e93195baa8acb92.webp?t=1716422916\" width=25 height=15 /></span>Controller support for 1-4 players.</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428300/extras/e514b2004c517a0a8e93195baa8acb92.webp?t=1716422916\" width=25 height=15 /></span>(at least one controller required for local multiplayer)</ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428300/extras/679e732c5cc9727baffb14d587399e52.avif?t=1716422916\" width=473 height=84 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428300/extras/60f1421c8912eff9a3dde23224899a43.p